Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
Yes, I think it is definitely good for the freshmen to live in the dorm, since the newbies can live together with older students, they can learn quickly about the the college, the major, the future career from the older, it is definitely better for the new.